Might be more of a "fun" spell, but not really practical IMHO. Frame rate hits in RvR are bad enough, I can imagine what that would do to it.<P>There are a few things I'd like to see...<P>Right now its really hard to get to some of our Frontier Keeps with all the high lvl mobs about. If your leaving from Sauvage, by the time you get out to try and defend, the battle is usually over. How about some kind of port spell direct to the Keeps? Might be more for other classes but what the hell, you can only try  <IMG SRC="smile.gif" border="0"> <P>The number one complaint people have (well one of the complaints) is pet down time. How about a small pet dmg sheild that is also a lifetap? Or a pet regen spell that drops when he enters combat?<P>Group mana regen spell? Group Endurance regen spell? MoB attack speed debuff? Party attack speed enhancment? Group levitate spell? Group infravision? Group underwater breathing...(oops sorry, wrong game  <IMG SRC="wink.gif" border="0"> )<P> - Hidien
