I have an idea, I just have no clue how feasible it is code wise, or how unbalancing it might be.<P>*Create Wall*<P>The spell would create an unpassable barrier 20 feet wide at the spot selected, perpindicular to the caster. The wall can not be passed physically by enemies, and cannot be shot through or targeted through by ANYONE, but can itself be targeted and destroyed. The chance to hit the wall is 100% regardless of level (who's gonna miss a wall?)<P>Matter Spec Line<BR>Level 5 - Wall of Straw 50 hp<BR>Level 15 - Wall of Sticks 150 hp<BR>Level 25 - Wall of Bricks 250 hp<BR>Level 35 - Wall of Granite 400 hp<BR>Level 45 - Wall of Power 1000 hp
