Here are some of my crackpot ideas for matter line.  Yes, some of them are prolly overpowered and need some editing and alot of them look like they would be fun (imo at least hehe) =p...spells:<P>Ponder: fast casting (2 secs or less) long range bolt- shoots question mark at target...if target doesnt resist target is mezzed for 3-6secs (depending on level of spell) and receives messages from himself (eg. "? what am I doing here?"  "? what is going on here? etc.)<P>Concussive Burst: short range shout ae with small dd and effects, 2min timer- all enemies lose current target and must retarget (retargetting cannot occur for 3-6secs depending on level of spell), causes vision to tunnel, screen to tilt back and forth, spin, etc, depending on level of spell.<P>Dissention: medium range single target, target goes berserk and attacks nearest target, friend or foe, for duration of spell (6-24secs based on spell level)<P>[Ethereal Form: short duration self-only shout buff, anyone that has you targetted loses target,  you cannot be targetted for 4-6 seconds, you cannot cast any other spells for first 3 seconds, 30min timer.]? *Prolly too good =p<BR>  <BR>AE Muddle: high power cost version of muddle type spell, w shorter duration (10-30secs?)...works on enemy players and npcs alike...possibly w slightly different effects..such as victims running in a random direction instead of attacking or healing enemy players?? etc<P>Strange Conviction:  fun spell w some practical uses (I think lol)...different versions of this spell...<BR>    strange conviction (chicken): ae spell causes victims to believe they are chickens- flapping arms, clucking and pecking at each other interuppting their spell casts and other attacks for every few seconds, duration  12-48secs.<BR>    strange conviction (cow): same as chicken but victims believe they are cows instead (mooing grazing etc) =P hehe <BR>    [strange conviction (lemming): victims follow caster around like lemmings, mimicking their actions/movements. duration 12-36secs] too powerful? 8)<P>Polymorph Other: victim turns into a toad for  30-60secs, special abilities such as spell casting/songs/ stealth etc cannot be used, melee can still be done but at reduced abilities (?)<P>Cursed Ground:  long casting (15secs +?), high power cose, caster can curse an area for a period of time causing any to enter to have a slight chance that they may begin to hallucinate or become muddled or mezzed for a short period of time.  area is clearly visible as cursed w floating skulls or tombstones, etc. 1 hour recast time.<P>Valentine's Friend:  summons an annoying lucradon (pet has 1hp, level 0, duration 10mins) which follows caster as a pet...has a special ability that it can detect stealthed enemies in vicinity: when it does it runs to them and proclaims its great affection for them, blowing kisses and chasing them around, following them making it impossible to stealth for 60secs at which time friend despawns<P>--------------------<P>Anonymous 38 Sorc Anon Server
